3. cs.RO (Robotics): The paper's focus on incremental reconstruction could be relevant to robotics applications where robots need to build maps of their environment in real-time. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper's focus on image-based 3D reconstruction could be relevant to multimedia applications such as virtual reality and augmented reality.
